00:52:34,519 --> 00:52:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] but it needs to not end there.

1875
00:52:37,480 --> 00:52:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] We need to look at financial extraction, you know, things like, you know,

1876
00:52:44,619 --> 00:52:49,139
